data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to 3175 Turret Dr, Kissimmee - Your POOL HOME Awaits!    Built in 2017, this exquisite 3-bedroom + loft, 2.5-bathroom POOL HOME boasts 2,307 square feet of luxurious living space on an OVER-SIZED LOT (2nd largest in neighborhood!) . You'll enjoy the enchanting outdoor space featuring: HEATED (electric) POOL, SCREEN ENCLOSURE, a serene POND VIEW, and to the right, a WOODED CONSERVATION area for eagles that adds to the natural beauty and tranquility of your surroundings.     WOOD-STYLE TILE flooring and UPDATED LIGHTING graces the entire first floor.  The built in  DECORATIVE FIREPLACE adds flair and elegance to the family room- with the option to heat the room, or just add visual ambiance.  The kitchen is adorned with GRANITE counters and UPGRADED cabinets, offering both style and functionality. Don't miss the generously sized WALK-IN PANTRY, ensuring that all your gourmet ingredients are within easy reach.    As you ascend to the second floor, you'll find a versatile LOFT AREA (which could be converted to a 4th bedroom), ideal for a home office, playroom, or additional entertainment space. The convenient UPSTAIRS LAUNDRY room simplifies that chore!     The primary bedroom is a true retreat, features a SOAKING TUB , and a walk-in "DRESSING-ROOM" CLOSET, complete with custom BUILT IN shelves, drawers and more to keep your wardrobe organized and stylish.    ADDITIONAL FEATURES: an ASSUMABLE 3.6% MORTGAGE,  a FENCED YARD ensuring privacy and security for your loved ones, and top-of-the-line finishes throughout the home.    About 20 minutes to the airport, 25 minutes to the parks, and 20 minutes to picturesque Downtown Kissimmee.  Schedule a showing today and experience the magic for yourself!
